Author: SanforizedJeans
Text: It happens. I'm vegan 100% of the time outside of binges, because my brain likes to give me *two* reasons to hate myself lmao. I honestly cannot stand places like that that have uncommon vegan options, but not the *most basic and easy to have on hand* ones. Like, why on *earth* does the cafe right by my apartment have vegan *cheesecake* of all things but *no* vegan milk options?????

Author: bitterviaproxy
Text: I did this last week when I ordered a cheese sandwich and a latte with almond milk 🤦‍♀️🤦‍♀️🤦‍♀️
